data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the town of Yelm with 4 bed/2.5 baths PLUS a bonus area upstairs! This home with A/C is in the heart of Yelm, one minute walk from the elementary school, and very close to JBLM and many amenities. It has such a wide variety of beautiful plants greeting you in the spring. Being on a cul de sac, this home has privacy and room for everyone to ride their bikes.  A spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances invites you into the open concept dining and living room. All appliances stay for a very easy moving experience. Come see this one before it's gone today!
